            <p class="w-5/6">Top 3 wheat-producing countries: <span class="font-bold italic">China, India</span> and <span class="font-bold italic">Russia.</span>
            <br>Top 3 wheat-consuming countries: <span class="font-bold italic">Europe, India</span> and <span class="font-bold italic">Russia/USA</span>.
            </p>
