              <svg fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945L3.055 11zM8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 004 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064L8 3.935zm7 16.553V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064L15 20.488zM21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke="#ecd2ac" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="w-5/6">Wheat is the <span class="font-bold">main ingredient in staple dishes</span> and baked goods around the world, like pasta, pizza, biscuits or bread products.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-12 flex justify-between">
            <div class="w-1/6 pr-8">
